// SAFETY: The caller is responsible for ensuring `user_data` is safe to send across
// thread boundaries. This is documented in `XbergEmbeddingBackendVTable` and the registration function.
unsafe impl Send for XbergEmbeddingBackendBridge {}
unsafe impl Sync for XbergEmbeddingBackendBridge {}

